#Event Viewer
Windows Event Viewer records all security-related activities.

## Important Event IDs
- 4625: Failed login attempt
- 4624: Successful login

## SOC Use Case
Multiple Event ID 4625 entries from the same IP indicate brute-force attacks.

## Analyst Actions
- Identify source IP
- Check targeted account
- Correlate with Event ID 4624
- Escalate if suspicious
